%% Diagram: Compositor three-tree state machine
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR
    [*] --> Main: cc receives commit
    Main --> Pending: push to pending tree
    Pending --> Pending: raster outstanding tiles
    Pending --> Active: activate when raster complete
    Active --> Active: scroll, transform,<br/>opacity animation
    Active --> [*]: replaced by next activation

    note right of Main
        Source of truth.
        Updated by main thread
        via Commit.
    end note
    note right of Pending
        Staging area while
        raster work is in flight.
        Not drawable yet.
    end note
    note right of Active
        Drawable. Survives until
        the next pending tree
        activates.
    end note
